<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>白龙山之家 · 家庭健身科普指南</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #ffffff;
    --bg-soft: #faf6ee;
    --paper: #ffffff;
    --ink: #2a2620;
    --ink-soft: #5a514a;
    --ink-light: #8a7f73;
    --accent: #8b3a2f;
    --accent-soft: #b9695a;
    --line: #e5dccc;
    --highlight: #f0e2c4;
    --serif: 'Noto Serif SC', 'Songti SC', 'STSong', serif;
    --sans: 'Noto Sans SC', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
  }

  body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ============ 布局 ============ */
  .layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ============ 左侧目录 ============ */
  .sidebar {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 48px 32px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .brand {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .brand-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .brand-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .toc {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .toc-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .toc li {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .toc a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 15px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    border-left: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .toc a:hover {
    background: #faf6ee;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .toc a.active {
    background: #faf6ee;
    color: var(--accent);
    border-left-color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .toc-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    min-width: 20px;
  }

  .toc a.active .toc-num {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* ============ 主内容区 ============ */
  .main {
    padding: 40px 80px 120px;
    max-width: 780px;
  }

  /* ============ 头部 ============ */
  .hero {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.25;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
  }

  .hero-meta span::before {
    content: "·";
    margin-right: 24px;
    color: var(--line);
  }

  .hero-meta span:first-child::before {
    display: none;
  }

  /* ============ 章节 ============ */
  section {
    margin-bottom: 96px;
    scroll-margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .chapter-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h4 {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  em {
    font-style: normal;
    background: linear-gradient(transparent 60%, var(--highlight) 60%);
    padding: 0 2px;
  }

  ul, ol {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  /* ============ 特殊组件 ============ */

  /* 章节配图 */
  .chapter-illust {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 0 32px 0;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #faf6ee;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 6;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .chapter-illust svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  /* 肌肉地图 - 大图 */
  .muscle-map {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 24px 0 40px;
    background: #faf6ee;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .muscle-map svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .muscle-map-caption {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-family: var(--serif);
  }

  /* 引用 / 重点框 */
  .callout {
    background: #faf6ee;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }

  .callout p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .callout-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* 误区卡片 */
  .myth {
    background: #faf6ee;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .myth-q {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .myth-q::before {
    content: "误区";
    font-size: 11px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-weight: 500;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .myth-a {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .myth-a strong {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* 好处列表 */
  .benefits {
    display: grid;
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .benefit {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .benefit:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .benefit-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .benefit-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .benefit-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* 肌群卡片 */
  .muscle {
    background: #faf6ee;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .muscle-name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .muscle-tag {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .muscle dl {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .muscle dt {
    color: var(--ink-light);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .muscle dd {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
  }

  /* 动作卡片 */
  .move {
    background: #faf6ee;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .move-gif {
    background: #faf6ee;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    font-size: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .move-gif img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .move-gif.placeholder {
    background-image: 
      linear-gradient(45deg, #ffffff 25%, transparent 25%),
      linear-gradient(-45deg, #ffffff 25%, transparent 25%),
      linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 75%, #ffffff 75%),
      linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 75%, #ffffff 75%);
    background-size: 20px 20px;
    background-position: 0 0, 0 10px, 10px -10px, -10px 0px;
  }

  .move-gif-label {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--line);
    font-family: var(--serif);
    color: var(--ink-light);
  }

  .move-content {
    padding: 24px 28px;
  }

  .move-name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .move-target {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .move-points {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .move-points li {
    padding-left: 24px;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .move-points li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .move-warn {
    background: #fdf4ee;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-soft);
  }

  .move-warn strong {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  /* 训练计划表 */
  .plan-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    background: #faf6ee;
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .plan-table th {
    background: #f0e7d4;
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 14px 12px;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--line);
  }

  .plan-table td {
    padding: 14px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  .plan-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .plan-table .week {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Q&A */
  .qa {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 24px 0;
  }

  .qa:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .qa-q {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .qa-q::before {
    content: "Q";
    font-family: var(--serif);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .qa-a {
    padding-left: 28px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* 数据强调 */
  .stat {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1em;
  }

  /* 页脚 */
  footer {
    margin-top: 96px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--ink-light);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  footer p {
    color: var(--ink-light);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* ============ 语言切换器 ============ */
  .lang-switcher {
    position: fixed;
    top: 16px;
    right: 16px;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .lang-switcher a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    transition: all 0.15s;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .lang-switcher a:hover {
    background: #faf6ee;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .lang-switcher a.active {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ============ 移动端导航按钮 ============ */
  .menu-toggle {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    top: 16px;
    left: 16px;
    z-index: 100;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    font-family: var(--sans);
  }

  .menu-toggle:hover {
    background: #faf6ee;
  }

  .overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    z-index: 90;
  }

  .overlay.active {
    display: block;
  }

  /* ============ 响应式 ============ */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 280px;
      height: 100vh;
      z-index: 95;
      transform: translateX(-100%);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 2px 0 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }

    .sidebar.active {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }

    .menu-toggle {
      display: block;
    }

    .main {
      padding: 64px 24px 80px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .hero-lead {
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 26px;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 19px;
    }

    body {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .myth, .muscle, .move-content {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .muscle dl {
      grid-template-columns: 70px 1fr;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .plan-table {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .plan-table th,
    .plan-table td {
      padding: 10px 8px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .main {
      padding: 56px 20px 60px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 23px;
    }

    section {
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }
  }

  /* 打印样式 */
  @media print {
    .sidebar, .menu-toggle, .overlay {
      display: none;
    }
    .layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .main {
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- 语言切换器 -->
<nav class="lang-switcher">
  <a href="index.html" class="active">中</a>
  <a href="en.html">EN</a>
  <a href="ru.html">RU</a>
</nav>

<button class="menu-toggle" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰ 目录</button>
<div class="overlay" onclick="toggleMenu()"></div>

<div class="layout">

  <!-- ============ 左侧目录 ============ -->
  <aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="brand-title">白龙山之家</div>
      <div class="brand-sub">家庭健身科普指南</div>
    </div>
    <div class="toc-label">目 录</div>
    <ul class="toc">
      <li><a href="#ch1" data-section="ch1"><span class="toc-num">01</span>为什么是现在</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch2" data-section="ch2"><span class="toc-num">02</span>五个常见误区</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch3" data-section="ch3"><span class="toc-num">03</span>力量训练的七大好处</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch4" data-section="ch4"><span class="toc-num">04</span>训练前的热身</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch5" data-section="ch5"><span class="toc-num">05</span>认识身体的四大肌群</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch6" data-section="ch6"><span class="toc-num">06</span>认识家庭健身房</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch7" data-section="ch7"><span class="toc-num">07</span>核心动作图解</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch8" data-section="ch8"><span class="toc-num">08</span>训练后拉伸</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch9" data-section="ch9"><span class="toc-num">09</span>12周入门计划</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch10" data-section="ch10"><span class="toc-num">10</span>吃什么</a></li>
      <li><a href="#ch11" data-section="ch11"><span class="toc-num">11</span>常见问题</a></li>
    </ul>
  </aside>

  <!-- ============ 主内容区 ============ -->
  <main class="main">

    <!-- 头部 -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">白 龙 山 之 家 · 家 庭 健 身 科 普 指 南</div>
      <h1>54岁,正是开始健身的好年纪</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">为什么这是开始训练的最好时机,以及如何在家中安全、有效地开始。</p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span>适合零基础</span>
        <span>家庭健身房</span>
        <span>循序渐进</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ============ 第一章 ============ -->
    <section id="ch1">
      <div class="chapter-num">第 一 章</div>
      <h2>为什么是现在</h2>

      <div class="chapter-illust">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 800 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="curveGrad" x1="0" x2="0" y1="0" y2="1">
              <stop offset="0" stop-color="#b9695a" stop-opacity="0.3"/>
              <stop offset="1" stop-color="#b9695a" stop-opacity="0"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <!-- 网格线 -->
          <g stroke="#d8cdb9" stroke-width="0.5" opacity="0.5">
            <line x1="80" y1="60" x2="760" y2="60"/>
            <line x1="80" y1="120" x2="760" y2="120"/>
            <line x1="80" y1="180" x2="760" y2="180"/>
            <line x1="80" y1="240" x2="760" y2="240"/>
          </g>
          <!-- 坐标轴 -->
          <line x1="80" y1="240" x2="760" y2="240" stroke="#5a514a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <line x1="80" y1="40" x2="80" y2="240" stroke="#5a514a" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <!-- 不训练的曲线 -->
          <path d="M 110 80 Q 250 90 380 130 T 720 220" fill="none" stroke="#8a7f73" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="6 4"/>
